replies.body:
Its not Champion Mains that drive toxicity its the concept of Main in general. How many games have you been in where someone's "main" gets banned, who "they only know how to play," and their entire capacity of being able to play mysteriously goes out the window like they've never played anyone else in the entirety of the game?


If we remove the illusion of "main" and simply learn all roles, everyone is better off for it. 

{{sticker:sona-playing}}
